      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>chive & crème fraîche sauce </strong>to one side of the plate and top with the <strong>lemon crumbed hake</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>roasted vegetables </strong>to the side and garnish with a <strong>lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
